   GPO Access User Support Team

   7:00 a.m. to 5:30 p.m. EST, Monday through Friday (except Federal
   holidays)
     * Toll-Free:    888-293-6498
     * DC Area:    202-512-1530
     * E-Mail:       gpoaccess@gpo.gov
     * Fax:           202-512-1262
     * Help us to help you

   Need help with your print publication and/or CD-ROM order?  Contact the
   GPO Order Desk, 7:30 a.m. to 4:30 p.m. EST, Monday through Friday
   (except Federal holidays) at:
     * Toll free:    866-512-1800
     * DC Area:   202-512-1800
     * Fax:          202-512-2250
     * E-mail:      orders@gpo.gov

   For additional help researching Federal information, contact your local
   Federal depository library.
